comment_regular_data.body:
@justinmk I love this idea. Honestly I think kickstart needs to die. It's an impossible project in some sense, because everyone has Strong Feelings about what it should be and they're often going in conflicting directions.

I'll look into these more minimal plugin managers. I am not married to lazy, and agree that the extra complexity isn't great.

One thing that I think is important though is that plugin authors provide instructions for configuration to match whichever one we pick.
